識或無意識咁去維護「司法獨立」呢副<del>招牌</del><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">搵食神主牌</span></span></strong></span>，話比人聽香港司法仍然獨立</blockquote>"}]}